'''Koodh''' waa shay ka mid ah [[dhar|dharka dumarku xidhaan]] kaasi oo dabacsan oo ka samaysan [[dun]], ama [[cudbi]], ama [[harag]] kaasi oo la tolay. Googaradu waay ka mid tahay [[dhar|dharka dadka]] kaasi oo inta badan loo xidho si jidhka uga difaaco [[Qaboow|dhaxan]]ta. Dharka waxaa laga sameeyaa dun ka timaada haraga [[xoolo|xoolaha]], [[xayawaan]]ka iyo [[cudbi]]ga iyo noocyo aartifishal ah. Marka dharka la samaynayo waxa la isticmaalaa habab badan oo kala duwan, waxaa ugu caansan tolida, mareegida, iyo isku xidhxidhka dunta.<ref>Barber, Elizabeth Wayland (1994). ''Women's Work. The first 20,000 Years'', p.135.Norton & Company, New York. {{ISBN|0-393-31348-4}}</ref> 
==Hordhac==
Googaradu waxay ka mid yahay dharka joogtada ah ee xidhaan dumarka [[Soomaali]]yeed isla markaana isticmaalaan kaasi oo loo xidho in jidhka ka difaaco dhaxanta iyo qaboowga. Sidoo kale, googarada waxaa loo xidhaa xarago iyo isqurxin.<ref>[https://somalilandblogtales.wordpress.com/2004/06/25/shopping-in-hargeisa/ Googarada xidhaan dumarka Soomaaliyeed maxay tahay?]</ref> Guud ahaan, googaradu waa maro la tolay taasi oo leh qaab le'eg qofka xidhanaya ama isticmaalaya sheygaasi. Googaradu wuxuu leeyahay astaamo u gaar ah oo ka duwan noocyada kale ee dharka. Astaamaha ugu muhiimsan ee shaadhasha waxaa ka mid ah jileec, fudeyd iyo gaabni le'eg kuraanta dusheeda.<ref>William L. Brown III, "Some Thoughts on Men's Shirts in America, 1750-1900", Thomas Publications, Gettysburg, PA 1999. {{ISBN|1-57747-048-6}}, p. 7</ref> 
==Magaca==
Ereyga '''''Googarad''''' asal ahaan lama yaqaano meel uu ka soo jeedo laakiin ilo ayaa ku tilmaamey ineey tahay Af-[[Hindi]].<ref>Dorothy K. Burnham, "Cut My Cote", Royal Ontario Museum, Toronto, Ontario 1973. {{ISBN|0-88854-046-9}}, p. 14</ref> 
==Dharka==
'''[[Dhar]]ka''' ({{lang-en|Textile ama Cloth}}; {{lang-ar|نسيج (قماش)}}) waa shay dabacsan oo ka samaysan [[dun]] la xardhay. Dharka waxaa laga sameeyaa dun ka timaada haraga [[xoolo|xoolaha]], [[xayawaan]]ka iyo [[cudbi]]ga iyo noocyo aartifishal ah.<ref>C. Willett and Phillis Cunnington, ''The History of Underclothes'', Dover Publications Inc., New York 1992. {{ISBN|0-486-27124-2}} pp. 23–25</ref> Marka dharka la samaynayo waxa la isticmaalaa habab badan oo kala duwan, waxaa ugu caansan tolida, mareegida, iyo isku xidhxidhka dunta. God ku yaala galbeedka wadanka Joorjiya ee bariga [[Yurub]] ayaa waxa laga helay qidcad harag oo lagu wado in dhar ahaan loo isticmaali jirey wakhti hada laga joogo 34,000 oo sano. Dharka guud ahaan waxaa la isku yidhaahdaa '''Hu<nowiki>'</nowiki>'''; kaasi oo u kala baxa noocyo badan. Kugu ugu muhiimsan ee dadku isticmaalaan maalin kasta waxaa ka mid ah: [[surwaal]]ka, [[shaadh]]ka, [[dirac]]a, [[shalmad]]a, [[goono (dhar)|goonada]], [[koodh (dhar)|koodhka]], [[kabbo|kabaha]] iyo kuwo kale oo badan.<ref>''"[[surwaal]]ka, [[shaadh]]ka, [[dirac]]a, [[shalmad]]a, [[goono (dhar)|goonada]], [[koodh (dhar)|koodhka]], [[kabbo|kabaha]]"''</ref><ref>C. Willett and Phillis Cunnington, ''The History of Underclothes'', Dover Publications Inc., New York 1992. {{ISBN|0-486-27124-2}} pp. 54</ref>

